    |  X INTERACT / PARACHUTE  |  Y POTION  |  START PAUSE  |  BACK / SELECT SHOP 
    |  REMAP: OVERVIEW > CONTROLS

    KEYBOARD: ARROWS / A-D MOVE  |  SHIFT RUN
